casebody.data:
Gary ROBINSON, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
Sabrina ROBINSON, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-2092 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. NOVEMBER 06, 2017 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and FERNANDEZ and LUCK, JJ., concur.

Upon the Court's own motion, it is ordered that this appeal from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida is dismissed for failure to comply with this Court's order dated September 29, 2017, and with the Florida Rules of Appellate Procedure.
